@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram (Plane Management)

[*] --> Order

state Order
Order : entry / Plane is placed in order
Order : do / Wait for delivery
Order : exit / Plane is delivered

Order --> Arrival

state Arrival
Arrival : entry / Plane arrives
Arrival : do / Transition to preparation
Arrival : exit / Plane is prepared

Arrival --> Preparation

state Preparation
Preparation : entry / Plane is prepared
Preparation : do / Assign to operations or maintenance
Preparation : exit / Plane is assigned

Preparation --> Operations
Preparation --> Maintenance

state Operations
Operations : entry / Plane is in operations
Operations : do / Check for scheduled flights
Operations : exit / Plane is still in operations

Operations --> Operations : Scheduled flights available

Operations --> Maintenance : No scheduled flights or maintenance required

state Maintenance
Maintenance : entry / Plane is in maintenance
Maintenance : do / Check and service plane
Maintenance : exit / Plane is ready for operations

Maintenance --> Preparation : Plane is ready for operations

state "Plane is no longer available" as NoLongerAvailable
NoLongerAvailable : entry / Plane is no longer available
NoLongerAvailable : do / Take plane out of service
NoLongerAvailable : exit / Plane is removed from operations

NoLongerAvailable --> End

state End <<choice>>
End --> [*]

@enduml
